casebody.data:
No. 104,

Misc.

Conklin v. Wainwright, Corrections Director. Earl Fair cloth, Attorney-General of Florida, and James McGuirk, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted, judgment of the United States Court of Appeals vacated, and case remanded to that court for a ruling on the merits.
